WEBVTT

00:05:57.909 --> 00:06:00.978
Shalon's daughter Soleil
is three years old now.

00:06:02.114 --> 00:06:03.915
She has a quick smile --

00:06:03.939 --> 00:06:06.545
every bit as brilliant
as her mother's was.

00:06:07.841 --> 00:06:09.676
Soleil is fearless.

00:06:09.700 --> 00:06:13.050
She's determined and she's so opinionated,

00:06:13.074 --> 00:06:14.075
(Laughter)

00:06:14.099 --> 00:06:15.586
so smart.

00:06:16.069 --> 00:06:18.949
Soleil constantly amazes me

00:06:18.973 --> 00:06:22.346
at how confidently
she is navigating her world.

00:06:23.703 --> 00:06:28.032
But Soleil only knows her mother
through photographs

00:06:28.056 --> 00:06:32.619
and the cherished memories that I have
and share with her every day.